Fillin Ta is the Whiphid co-owner of Gep's Grill in Mos Eisley. He met Norun Gep, his partner, in jail when they were street urchins. They have remained friends and business partners even since.

Usually the two Whiphids get the meat for their business from hunters, but when the hunts have been bad, the local stables have been known to get a visit from two Whiphids. Besides running their grill, the Whiphids also run a small smuggling business that hasn't gained the attention of Jabba Desilijic Tiure.
